Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE EYE JEWEL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you shall slowly feel my wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've come up\Nwith an entertaining idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must serve beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Surface World is demolished,\NI shall keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can watch this Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the hope of the Surface World,\Nbe viciously torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then spend the rest of your life\Nserving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be an Underworld songstress,\Nsinging of my power and terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be much more entertaining\Nthan just simply slaughtering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can enjoy that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! If Dai should fall,\Nthen I won't live long either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight until the very end\Ntogether with Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For one so young\Nto possess such a strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never encountered this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at your precious Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no if. He will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to kill him, I want him\Ncompletely and utterly destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to see my greatness\Nand the limits of his own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And to see the true nature\Nof the humans he so loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He should know true despair\Nbefore he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Princess, take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your Hero get pummeled to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai?! Can't you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to roll around\Nlike a worm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps my Calamity End\Nwas too powerful?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! I can't move properly!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get up! Fight back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I must watch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't avert my eyes\Nfrom Dai's suffering.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fighting, too!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something! Anything!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything against the Dark King!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just doing that\Nwill lessen Dai's suffering!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Kaiser Phoenix!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be wounded\Nby a little girl, Dark King?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban's body couldn't be cut\Nby even a Gigastrash,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but unless he's fully focused,\Nhe can't maintain his invulnerability!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I could wound him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in this world is invulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still want to keep me alive\Nthen go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell everyone\Nfor the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wounded the great Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm the strongest woman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Get up! Stand up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't stand...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then Leona will...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will regret that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can no longer resist or speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona became a jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel, Princess Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?! What happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided to wound me,\Nso I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be satisfied\Nunless you suffer a fate worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've used my Magic Power\Nto turn you into a jewel called an Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only three things\Nyou can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, hear, and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot move,\Nand your voice cannot be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what scenes of atrocity\Nmay unfold before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,While heavily wounded,\Nyou may still be worthy of fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now watch from there, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as the Hero is beaten beyond all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot fight with him,\Nnor can you take your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As a leader of the Surface World,\Nthere can be no greater humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will change you back once you decide\Nto pledge eternal servitude to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn her back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to stop my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat me and she'll be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But that seems unlikely in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to defeat Ban!\NIf I don't defeat him here, then Leona...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But his Tenchimato is perfect.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has no weakness!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! If there's no weakness, then...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That look... He's thought of something.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't do it alone!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's wrong? Didn't you think of\Nsome way to fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You will still be torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calamity End?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenchimato
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't necessary for a Kaiser Phoenix\Nor Calamity Wall attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The divine power of my palm strike\Ncan also be unleashed at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why use my ultimate skill against\None who has lost the will to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Dai. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely even stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To be powerless at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To be forced to just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Princess! I feel your torment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To feel it for just a minute,\Nfor just a second longer is more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that my last attack\Nwas just a simple palm strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Calamity End is my greatest strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I put all of my might into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you withstand a second one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity End!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}MINAKATOR{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}THE DEMONIC GUARD OF HEAVEN AND EARTH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity End!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Mister Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to beat all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over until you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You little scrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, everyone! That eye is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like most of you were\Nbarely healthy enough to make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those worthy enough to fight me are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, Popp, Aban, Hym, Larhart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When hit by the light\Nof Ban's third eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone too weak to fight\Nis turned into a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He got Leona, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everyone's in these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrifying Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To come all this way and be useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Hyunckel was already\Nin critical condition.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam and Brokin were still wounded\Nfrom the fight with Myst.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sadly, I guess Big Guy and Chiu\Nweren't strong enough.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a big difference\Nbetween Big Guy and Chiu.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I guess compared to Ban\Nit's all the same.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they still alive in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But they can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. That's actually better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't you care\Nthat he got your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be turned back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban said defeating him\Nwould restore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Dark King.\NWe won't be able to cover for our wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it,\Nthose jewels won't break so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam and the Princess are actually safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to worry about\Ngetting thrown off by them getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little heartless,\Nbut defeating him will be easier this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so noisy,\Nso I thought you'd be more sympathetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can be pretty level-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if we lose,\Nthe Surface World is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And our friends won't be turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Matorif?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means defeating him,\Nand saving our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been instructing Popp\Nwhile I was gone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like back then.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like Matorif\Nis right here beside me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before you know it,\Nthey've all grown up so much.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cool. Be cool!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now's the time to fight like Mentor!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that we know he can reflect Medoroa,\NI've only got one thing left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's this sharp mind that's got me\Nand my friends through numerous perils!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose\Nthe bigger the audience the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to see the fall of the Hero Dai,\Nhope of the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should all be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are witnesses to history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry, heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Howl, earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the age of darkness has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... witness this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heal Master Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...to hold him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't charge into his Tenchimato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Dark King's ultimate skill!\NNot even the three of you could...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Popp?!\NWe have to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hakendisutoru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aura Knuckle!{i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tenchimato!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the three of you\Ntogether can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At least Dai's Gigastrash\Nmanaged to wound me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw it! He repelled the Hakendisutoru\Nwith the force of his palm...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}took down the Aban Strash\Nwith Kaiser Phoenix...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and shattered the Aura Knuckle\Nwith a palm strike!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attack, defense, and magic\Nall in one motion!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's Ban's ultimate skill!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did you abandon them all, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban's stance is unbeatable!\NI know that, which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! They're alive!\NWe have to stop them from--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why doesn't he finish them?\NThey're all in shambles!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He could wipe them all out\Nwith a single extreme spell!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he playing with them?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's not it.\NHe isn't giving any openings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give up and beg for your lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you once again\Nface my ultimate skill of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Given that choice,\Nthere is but one answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take our chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A welcome answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like one of you\Nwon't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased that\Nyou fell so quickly, Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting power aside,\Nyour brain can't be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the smartest man on the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you,\Nthere's still someone smarter than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you held Dai back\Ndespite knowing what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Hero's strike\Ncan defeat the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were following the advice\Nthat I gave to Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Dai, the Hero is the only one\Nwho can defeat the Dark King,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one who can unlock\NDai's full potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one who has been with him\Nsince the very beginning of this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Work together... and achieve victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Aban was turned into an Eye Jewel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and his friends\Nare helplessly battered.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And his allies trapped in Eye Jewels\Ncan do nothing but cry out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things are dire, and to overcome\Nthe Dark King's greatest skill,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Demonic Guard of Heaven and Earth,\NPopp readies a desperate plan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.35,0:23:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"On This Bond"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
